tool_description: This Read-Only API Allows Users To Access Their Sleeper Fantasy Football Leagues. Lookup Leagues, Check Standings, View Keeper Options And More.
title: Satellite API

api_list.name: DIVISION BATTLE
api_list.description: Returns the sum of the player scores in each division for the current week. *Optionally post the results to GroupMe.*
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://satellite-api.p.rapidapi.com/division/{league_id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "satellite-api.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

api_list.name: LOOKUP
api_list.description: Lookup active Sleeper leagues for a given username.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://satellite-api.p.rapidapi.com/lookup/{username}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "satellite-api.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
